<p><strong>8. Registered Users, subscriptions and cancellations</strong></p>
<p style="margin-left: 35.45pt;">8.1 In order to register on the Olympiad Foundation website you must be either a qualified teacher or an international school.</p>
<p style="margin-left: 35.45pt;">8.2 You may register your profile for free and will have access to most of our services. Subscription charges are levied to gain full access to the service for schools, including but not limited to the ability to contact teachers. Subscription is entirely voluntary and you may remain a free Registered User as long as you wish. There are no subscription charges for teachers.</p>
<p>8.3 Olympiad Foundation may change the subscription pricing, options, renewal terms or Registered User services at any time. The Registered User may cancel their subscription at any time. School subscription fees are not transferable from one Registered User profile to another.</p>
